# If you want to keep the data/ and dashboard/ folder but ignore specific files, you might adjust this.
# But for a showcase, we typically DO commit the data and pbix if they are small enough (under 50MB).
# So I will NOT ignore pbix and xlsx by default here, so you can push them to GitHub.

# Ignore large data files (uncomment if data > 100MB)
# data/*.xlsx
# data/*.csv

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.log
